
Setup (do once!)
----------------

* cd /where/you/cloned/pts
* e=~/.venv/pts # or another environment
* module sw python python3
* python3 -m venv --system-site-packages $e  # create environment
* source $e/bin/activate  # load environment
* python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt


Run
---

* cd /where/you/cloned/pts
* source $e/bin/activate  # load environment (if not done yet)
* ./pts --help
* ./pts msl_05L_ELSA_2021070300 out.grib --distance=2.0e5

